{"tid":1586283,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警取手令　九巴交部分八達通交易記錄及閉路電視片段","createTime":"2019-09-22T01:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T03:06:51.000Z","uid":36122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1b4bf0e783e8910e73ad274299a4c5773c485a22","tid":1586283,"uid":36122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T01:19:55.000Z","msg":"消息指，警方取得法庭手令，就近日反修例風波示威活動，要求九巴交出八達通交易記錄資料。<br />\n<br />\n據瞭解，警方近日取得相關法庭手令，九巴根據手令內容，交出指定日子、時間及班次，巴士上的八達通交易記錄以及車上的閉路電視片段。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1481807-20190921.htm?fbclid=IwAR0YncMO-HoRTmBRpj9kgoLEc5xtNqCmEX2wbnc58cdISXLjrQ8KNU0NxGE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1481807-20190921.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0YncMO-HoRTmBRpj9kgoLEc5xtNqCmEX2wbnc58cdISXLjrQ8KNU0NxGE&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FYc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=1f968925\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1481807-20190921.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0YncMO-HoRTmBRpj9kgoLEc5xtNqCmEX2wbnc58cdISXLjrQ8KNU0NxGE&h=897a53ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1481807-20190921.htm?fbclid=IwAR0YncMO-HoRTmBRpj9kgoLEc5xtNqCmEX2wbnc58cdISXLjrQ8KNU0NxGE</a><br />\n<br />\n大家上巴士都要小心啊!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739e6d9c78c382faebd9573618f3af3402b13111","tid":1586283,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T03:06:51.000Z","msg":"死黑警， 又喺度 打壓民眾"}]}